Instalar o PYGAME

sudo apt-get install python-pygame

Instalar o Pip

sudo apt-get install python-pip

* Se precisar atualizar o pip: pip install --upgrade pip

Instalar o PyOpenGL

pip install --user PyOpenGL PyOpenGL_accelerate

Instalar Python Imaging Library

pip install --user Pillow

sudo apt-get install python-dev libjpeg-dev libfreetype6-dev zlib1g-dev

sudo apt-get install python-imaging


Installar o NumPY

sudo apt-get install python-numpy

-----------------------

Caso ocorra algum problema em importar OpenGL.GL instale:

sudo apt-get install python python-numpy python-opengl python-qt4 python-qt4-gl

-----------------------

Pra rodar o programa:

.../fretsonfire/src

python FretsOnFire.py